给定两个[[函数]]$$f_{1}(t),f_{2}(t)$$，记$$F_{1}(\omega)=\mathscr{F} [f_{1}(t)],F_{2}(\omega)=\mathscr{F} [f_{2}(t)]$$，则

$$
\mathscr{F} [f_{1}(t) \ast f_{2}(t)] = F_{1}(\omega)\cdot F_{2}(\omega)
$$

即[[傅里叶变换]]将[[卷积]]变换为[[乘积|乘法]]。

对偶地，[[傅里叶变换]]将乘积变换为卷积：

$$
\mathscr{F} [f_{1}(t) \cdot f_{2}(t)] = F_{1}(\omega)\ast F_{2}(\omega)
$$
